description:
Dragon's Teeth!

A man can go to any lengths to escape an object he hates or dreads -- only to find he has merely run a circle!

TNT Bait!

How does it feel to be a fish on a hook? Champion fisherman John Prentice never knew until he fought an enemy who hooked him!

Balloon Ace!

He was within one plane of becoming the first member of his squadron to down five Boche Planes --- but he deliberately fired the other way... Balloon Ace!

Medic Detective (Text only story)

Jump Boots!

You'll never forget the time you first got them -- how you shined them up until you could see your face in them -- how you felt prouder than any G.I. in the Army -- wearing them! They -- you had to earn them!
name: Dragon's Teeth!; TNT Bait!; Balloon Ace!; Medic Detective; Jump Boots!
